&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Headquartered in New York City, our culture has been recognized by Inc Magazine as a &quot;Best Workplace,” by Crain’s NY as a &quot;Best Places to Work in NYC,&quot; and as one of the 10 hottest SaaS startups in New York for two years in a row. Most recently, SecurityScorecard was named to Fast Company’s annual list of the&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://securityscorecard.com/blog/blog-top-innovators-of-the-year/&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;World’s Most Innovative Companies for 2023&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt; and to the Achievers 50 Most Engaged Workplaces in 2023 award recognizing “forward-thinking employers for their unwavering commitment to employee engagement.”&amp;nbsp; SecurityScorecard is proud to be funded by world-class investors including Silver Lake Waterman, Moody’s, Sequoia Capital, GV and Riverwood Capital.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Team:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;SecurityScorecard is seeking a highly motivated and experienced Senior Director of Demand Generation with 7-10 years of proven expertise in demand generation strategies. The ideal candidate will have a background in the cybersecurity industry and a track record of successfully driving demand and revenue growth. As the Senior Director of Demand Generation, you will play a pivotal role in developing and executing comprehensive demand generation programs to fuel our sales pipeline and accelerate the company&#39;s growth.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;About the Role:&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demand Generation Strategy: Develop and execute a robust demand generation strategy to drive awareness, engagement, and demand for SecurityScorecard&#39;s cybersecurity solutions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Account-Based Marketing (ABM): Leverage ABM techniques to target high-value accounts, collaborating closely with sales and marketing teams to create personalized campaigns tailored to each account.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Multi-Channel Campaigns: Plan and execute multi-channel demand generation campaigns, including email marketing, digital advertising, social media, webinars, events, and content marketing, to generate high-quality leads and nurture existing leads through the sales funnel.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Data-Driven Approach: Utilize data and analytics to measure campaign effectiveness, identify opportunities for optimization, and provide actionable insights to stakeholders.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Sales Collaboration: Work closely with the sales team to align demand generation activities with sales objectives, ensuring seamless integration between marketing and sales efforts.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Global Campaign Strategy and Content Development: Collaborate with the product marketing, content and creative teams to develop compelling, audience-specific content and messaging that resonates with target audiences.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Budget Management: Manage the demand generation budget effectively, ensuring maximum ROI from marketing investments.&lt;/li&gt;
